// submit мҷ„лЈҢ нӣ„ лӢӨмқҢ мІҳлҰ¬ мӢӨн–үн•ҳкё° мң„н•ҙ callback кө¬нҳ„
scwin.hmhnoCallback = null;
scwin.f_loadHmhno = function (param, callback) {
  scwin.hmhnoCallback = callback || null;
  dma_hmhno_search.set("sysCd", "ilCommonEBC");
  dma_hmhno_search.set("queryId", "retriveSeaMasterMhnoListCombo");
  dma_hmhno_search.set("param1", param);
  $c.sbm.execute($p, sbm_hmhno);
};
scwin.mmhnoCallback = null;
scwin.f_loadMmhno = function (param, callback) {
  scwin.mmhnoCallback = callback || null;
  dma_mmhno_search.set("sysCd", "ilCommonEBC");
  dma_mmhno_search.set("queryId", "retriveSeaHouseMhnoListCombo");
  dma_mmhno_search.set("param1", param);
  dma_mmhno_search.set("param2", cnd_lc_iogb.getValue());
  $c.sbm.execute($p, sbm_mmhno);
};
scwin.sbm_hmhno_submitdone = function (e) {
  if (scwin.hmhnoCallback) {
    scwin.hmhnoCallback();
    scwin.hmhnoCallback = null;
  }
  ds_hmhno.setRowPosition(0);
};
scwin.sbm_mmhno_submitdone = function (e) {
  if (scwin.mmhnoCallback) {
    scwin.mmhnoCallback();
    scwin.mmhnoCallback = null;
  }
  ds_mmhno.setRowPosition(0);
};
scwin.ds_correctionNotice_onrowpositionchange = function (rowIndex, oldRow) {
  let vRowPosition = ds_correctionNotice.getRowPosition();
  let vRowStatus = ds_correctionNotice.getRowStatusValue(vRowPosition);
  if (vRowPosition >= 0) {
    if (vRowStatus === 0) {
      // мӣҗліё мғҒнғң 
      $c.gus.cfDisableBtnOnly($p, [btn_Print, btn_Create, btn_Update, btn_Cancel, btn_Save, btn_Delete]);
      $c.gus.cfEnableBtnOnly($p, [btn_Print, btn_Create, btn_Update, btn_Delete]);
      scwin.processFlag = "RETRIEVE";
    } else if (vRowStatus === 2) {
      // мӢ к·ң мғқм„ұ
      scwin.f_Set("CREATE");
    } else if (vRowStatus === 1) {
      // м—…лҚ°мқҙнҠё(к°ұмӢ )
      scwin.f_Set("UPDATE");
    }
  } else {
    scwin.f_Set("INIT");
    scwin.processFlag = "INIT";
  }
};

